    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from what it says to what the author intended in his original context and what it contributes to the canon's unfolding argument. The movements below follow the chapter's own logical structure: the Lord's indictment, the covenantal diagnosis, the command to build, the community's obedient response, and the divine enabling. Hebrew word studies follow in blockquotes as supplements, not the spine.",
